<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>النَّكَفَتَان، وَالغُنْدُبَتَان <span class="c2">(مُثَنَّى غُنْدُوَة)</span>: اللَّوْزَتَان ٠<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
